  "HomeWiki": "<div class=\"wikidoc\">\r\n<p><strong>Project Description</strong><br>\r\nRole Based Access Control<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nsee a diagram &gt;&gt; <a href=\"/wikipage?title=Design&referringTitle=Home\">Design</a>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>features:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Integration with HttpModule<br>\r\n2. Easy to configurate<br>\r\n3. No need to learn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>requirment:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Sql Server 2008<br>\r\n2. Ado.Net Entity Framework 4<br>\r\n4. Visual Studio 2010<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>how to start administry:</strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Open RBAC/RBAC.edmx.sql and execute.<br>\r\n2. Configurate RBAC.Administry/Web.config/connection string/EntityContext, set it up as your local place.<br>\r\n3. Run.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>how to integrate</strong></p>\r\n<p>1. Make sure that your web application is authentication = Forms<br>\r\n2. Configurate YourApp/Web.config/System.Web/</p>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">httpModules</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">add</span> <span style=\"color:red\">name</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">AccessControlModule</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">type</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">RBAC.AccessControlModule, RBAC</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">httpModules</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br>\r\n3. Add configuration section</p>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">configSections</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">section</span> <span style=\"color:red\">name</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">rbac</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">type</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">RBAC.Config.AccessControlSection, RBAC</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">configSections</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br>\r\n................</p>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">rbac</span> <span style=\"color:red\">turn</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">on</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">connection</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">rbac</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span> <span style=\"color:red\">system</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">front</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ignores</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">add</span> <span style=\"color:red\">path</span><span style=\"color:blue\">=</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">/login.aspx</span><span style=\"color:black\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color:blue\">/&gt;</span>\n    <span style=\"color:green\">&lt;!--&lt;add path=&quot;more...&quot;/&gt;--&gt;</span>\n  <span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">ignores</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n<span style=\"color:blue\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#a31515\">rbac</span><span style=\"color:blue\">&gt;</span>\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<p><br>\r\n4. Apply reference of RBAC assembly to your application.</p>\r\n</div><div class=\"ClearBoth\"></div>",
